ViewObject.SQLQuery: select PermitHeaderEO.Addtl_chrgs, PermitHeaderEO.Admin_Chrgs, PermitHeaderEO.Appl_date, PermitHeaderEO.Assg_Reason_ID, PermitHeaderEO.Assigned_By, PermitHeaderEO.Assigned_On, PermitHeaderEO.Assigned_To, PermitHeaderEO.Auto_Renew_Flag, PermitHeaderEO.Changed_flag, PermitHeaderEO.City_Code, PermitHeaderEO.Country_Code, PermitHeaderEO.Created_By, PermitHeaderEO.Created_Date, PermitHeaderEO.Cust_ID, gim.CUST_NAME customer_name, gim.Mobile_num Mobile_num, PermitHeaderEO.DoT_Approval_Status, PermitHeaderEO.DoT_Approved_Date, PermitHeaderEO.DoT_Approved_by, PermitHeaderEO.DoT_Insp_Comments, PermitHeaderEO.Emirates_id, PermitHeaderEO.Existing_Permit_count, PermitHeaderEO.Inst_Quota_seq, PermitHeaderEO.Issue_date, PermitHeaderEO.Last_Assg_Note, PermitHeaderEO.LastUndoableOperation, PermitHeaderEO.UTIL_BILL_NUM, PermitHeaderEO.PRM_APPL_NUM, PermitHeaderEO.PRM_Header_seq, PermitHeaderEO.Paid_flag, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Chrgs, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_End_date, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Number, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Refund_Amt, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Remarks, PermitHeaderEO.Categ_code, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Status_ID, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_Type, PermitHeaderEO.Local_Flag, PermitHeaderEO.Permit_start_date, PermitHeaderEO.Prm_duration, PermitHeaderEO.Proc_Chrgs, PermitHeaderEO.Sector_Code, PermitHeaderEO.Updated_by, PermitHeaderEO.Updated_date, PermitHeaderEO.renewal_count, PermitHeaderEO.vhl_plate_id, PermitHeaderEO.permit_type permit_typename, PermitHeaderEO.status_name status_name, PermitHeaderEO.plate_number plate_number, PermitHeaderEO.plate_country plate_country, PermitHeaderEO.plate_category plate_category, PermitHeaderEO.plate_type plate_type, PermitHeaderEO.Floor_Number, PermitHeaderEO.Lessor_Name, PermitHeaderEO.Mobile_Number, PermitHeaderEO.Nationality, PermitHeaderEO.Number_Of_Bedrooms, PermitHeaderEO.Owner_Name, PermitHeaderEO.Owner_Tawtheeq_ID, PermitHeaderEO.Response_Code, PermitHeaderEO.Response_Desc, PermitHeaderEO.Sector_Name_AR, PermitHeaderEO.Tenant_Name, PermitHeaderEO.Tenant_Tawtheeq_ID, PermitHeaderEO.Unit_Number, PermitHeaderEO.Unit_Type, PermitHeaderEO.Tawtheeq_Int_Status, PermitHeaderEO.Actual_Usage, PermitHeaderEO.Property_Type, PermitHeaderEO.Contract_Expiry_Date, PermitHeaderEO.Premise_Number, PermitHeaderEO.Premise_Info, PermitHeaderEO.Contract_Number from (select ph.Addtl_chrgs, ph.Admin_Chrgs, ph.Appl_date, ph.Assg_Reason_ID, ph.Assigned_By, ph.Assigned_On, ph.Assigned_To, ph.Auto_Renew_Flag, ph.Changed_flag, ph.City_Code, ph.Country_Code, ph.Created_By, ph.Created_Date, ph.Cust_ID, ph.DoT_Approval_Status, ph.DoT_Approved_Date, ph.DoT_Approved_by, ph.DoT_Insp_Comments, ph.Emirates_id, ph.Existing_Permit_count, ph.Inst_Quota_seq, ph.Issue_date, ph.Last_Assg_Note, ph.LastUndoableOperation, ph.UTIL_BILL_NUM, ph.PRM_APPL_NUM, ph.PRM_Header_seq, ph.Paid_flag, ph.Permit_Chrgs, ph.Permit_End_date, ph.Permit_Number, ph.Permit_Refund_Amt, ph.Permit_Remarks, ph.Categ_code, ph.Permit_Status_ID, ph.Permit_Type, ph.Local_Flag, ph.Permit_start_date, ph.Prm_duration, ph.Proc_Chrgs, pvs.Sector_Code, ph.Updated_by, ph.Updated_date, ph.renewal_count,ph.vhl_plate_id, ph.permit_type permit_typename, ph.Floor_Number, ph.Lessor_Name, ph.Mobile_Number, ph.Nationality, ph.Number_Of_Bedrooms, ph.Owner_Name, ph.Owner_Tawtheeq_ID, ph.Response_Code, ph.Response_Desc, ph.Sector_Name_AR, ph.Tenant_Name, ph.Tenant_Tawtheeq_ID, ph.Unit_Number, ph.Unit_Type, ph.Tawtheeq_Int_Status, ph.Actual_Usage, ph.Property_Type, ph.Contract_Expiry_Date, ph.Premise_Number, ph.Premise_Info, ph.Contract_Number, pst.status_name status_name, vpm.plate_number plate_number,vpm.plate_cnt_id plate_country, vpm.plate_ctg_id plate_category, vpm.plate_type_id plate_type FROM PRM_Header ph, prm_permit_type_mst pt, prm_permit_status_mst pst, veh_plate_mst vpm, prm_vhl_sectors pvs Where pt.Type_code = ph.permit_type and pt.Categ_code = ph.Categ_code AND pst.status_id = ph.permit_status_id AND vpm.plate_id = ph.vhl_plate_id AND ph.prm_header_seq = pvs.prm_header_seq ) PermitHeaderEO left outer join (select inst_id as cust_id,INST_NAME as CUST_NAME,''as Mobile_num from GEN_INSTITUTION_MST union select cust_id,first_name as CUST_NAME,Mobile_num from GEN_customer_MST )gim on gim.cust_id = PermitHeaderEO.cust_id
